Give us your take.

03:51.406 --> 03:52.472
Yeah, it's been, uh, very similar.

03:52.540 --> 03:54.240
You know, uh, uh, consistent.

03:54.309 --> 03:56.275
Actually, no. I'm sorry, I mean similar.

03:56.344 --> 03:58.311
No... I'm-I'm sorry. I mean consistent.

03:58.379 --> 04:01.380
Whatever. Wha... Whatever, man. (LAUGHS)

04:01.483 --> 04:04.150
(TANDY AND TODD LAUGH)

04:04.219 --> 04:05.711
So, hey, Karl.

04:05.736 --> 04:07.941
So w-whatcha you been
getting up to, uh,

04:07.966 --> 04:09.899
you know, uh, location-wise?

04:09.962 --> 04:12.892
Oh, I was just, um, out at a graveyard.

04:12.917 --> 04:15.584
(STAMMERING) So-so-so
you don't say?

04:15.717 --> 04:17.396
You don't say? Huh?

04:17.464 --> 04:21.233
Well, uh... and what were you
doing, on-on earth, out there?

04:21.302 --> 04:22.535
Well, I've been pretty stressed lately.

04:22.604 --> 04:24.537
Well, that's the logical
place for a mental reboot,

04:25.210 --> 04:26.685
- is what that is.
- Yeah.

04:26.710 --> 04:28.174
I needed to clear my head.

04:28.243 --> 04:30.153
Recenter myself.

04:30.178 --> 04:31.536
Now, Karl...

04:31.561 --> 04:32.919
KARL: Mm-hmm?

04:32.944 --> 04:36.315
What would you say if I
told you that Todd and I

04:36.384 --> 04:40.733
were at that there, that,
uh, cemetery tonight?

04:40.823 --> 04:42.857
Well, what did you see out there?

04:42.882 --> 04:46.521
Uh, from where we were perched,

04:46.546 --> 04:48.561
uh, we noticed, uh, you know,

04:48.630 --> 04:50.596
something rather alarming.

04:50.698 --> 04:53.566
Eh, stupefying, even.

04:53.635 --> 04:55.334
You did?

04:55.403 --> 04:58.337
See, looked to us...

04:58.406 --> 05:01.140
like maybe you had dug
your little fingie-wingies

05:01.209 --> 05:03.309
into a little cadavey-wavvy,

05:03.378 --> 05:08.114
and then took a teeny eeny
weenie little bitesy-witesy.

05:08.183 --> 05:09.248
(ERICA CLICKS TONGUE)

05:09.715 --> 05:10.948
KARL: Mm-hmm.

05:11.141 --> 05:14.810
And you want to sort of know
what that was all about, huh?

05:15.892 --> 05:17.290
Yeah.

05:17.358 --> 05:21.015
Look, the quick answer is: yeah.

05:21.119 --> 05:23.953
I took a couple little nibbles.

05:24.060 --> 05:26.409
Okay, I'm just gonna
come right out and say it.

05:26.434 --> 05:28.267
(EXHALES)

05:28.336 --> 05:31.404
My name is Karl, and I am a cannibal.

05:31.472 --> 05:34.373
- (GASPS)
- Oh, God, yes.

05:34.442 --> 05:36.475
It's like a weight has been lifted.

05:36.544 --> 05:39.171
Anyway, this has been such a day.

05:39.196 --> 05:41.214
So why don't we all get some sleep,

05:41.316 --> 05:43.349
and we can pick this up in the morning.

05:43.418 --> 05:45.203
It'll give you, uh, time

05:45.228 --> 05:48.990
to process this and formulate
some questions for me.

05:49.030 --> 05:51.617
And hey, I'm gonna have
some questions for you.

05:51.695 --> 05:52.827
It's a two-way street.

05:52.834 --> 05:54.043
This is a dialogue.

05:54.087 --> 05:56.020
Good people on both sides.

05:56.300 --> 05:58.003
All right. Well, good night, guys.

05:58.028 --> 06:00.662
Lock your doors. Mean that.

