right now, if you're up for it.

06:30.999 --> 06:32.933
Sure thing, Jelly Bean.

06:41.918 --> 06:43.960
It's bugging you, isn't it?

06:47.950 --> 06:49.182
Aw.

06:49.284 --> 06:51.251
Thank you.

06:56.992 --> 06:59.793
I realize it might be hard
for you to drink in that thing,

06:59.876 --> 07:01.876
so I brought you this crazy...

07:02.292 --> 07:06.292
I mean, "mentally abnormal" straw.

07:09.167 --> 07:11.126
(LAUGHS NERVOUSLY)

07:18.498 --> 07:20.276
Oh, nice.

07:21.283 --> 07:22.849
- Carol?
- Yeah?

07:22.918 --> 07:24.050
- (SHOUTING MANIACALLY)
- (SCREAMS)

07:24.119 --> 07:25.952
- (SHOTGUN COCKS)
- Whoa! Hey!

07:26.021 --> 07:27.829
(CHUCKLING) I gotcha there.

07:27.868 --> 07:31.224
Sorry. Oh, it's too soon.
It's too soon. I'm sorry.

07:31.293 --> 07:33.059
In all seriousness, though,
you're gonna want to keep

07:33.128 --> 07:34.261
a five-foot radius.

07:34.329 --> 07:36.272
That's what I call the lunge zone.

07:36.397 --> 07:38.064
Noted.

07:38.795 --> 07:40.867
Okay, I know what you guys are thinking.

07:40.936 --> 07:42.068
Is it a problem?

07:42.309 --> 07:44.309
Sure, yeah, big-time problem.

07:44.373 --> 07:46.873
So, let's get into it.

07:46.942 --> 07:49.943
D-Do you want to kill us?

07:50.012 --> 07:52.879
Do I want to kill you? Well...

07:52.948 --> 07:54.730
that's why I came back here.

07:54.755 --> 07:55.746
- GAIL: What the...?
- (ALL GROANING)

07:55.771 --> 07:57.824
