08:07.362 --> 08:11.064
I do want to kill you,<i> but...</i>

08:11.133 --> 08:13.635
See, the pause works better
there, after the "but." But...

08:13.667 --> 08:15.585
I wanted you to know
that I wanted to kill you

08:15.600 --> 08:17.915
before I <i> did</i> kill you.

08:17.940 --> 08:19.039
This making sense?

08:19.141 --> 08:20.944
- No.
- Not really.

08:21.694 --> 08:25.045
I've-I've battled a lot
of demons in my life.

08:25.125 --> 08:27.001
But after spending all
that time in prison,

08:27.049 --> 08:29.115
I thought I had them beat.

08:29.218 --> 08:32.219
And I'm finding out now
that maybe I'm not as strong

08:32.287 --> 08:34.821
as I... I hoped I'd be.

08:34.923 --> 08:36.804
So you don't want to kill us?

08:37.258 --> 08:40.159
I desperately don't want to kill you.

08:40.229 --> 08:42.162
But you might kill us anyway?

08:42.568 --> 08:43.974
I mean...

08:43.999 --> 08:46.867
Karl, could you give us one sec?

08:46.935 --> 08:48.068
