08:55.043 --> 08:57.177
- We're not J.K. Rowling.
- I-I got it.

08:57.246 --> 08:59.683
You know, when I was a kid, my
dad caught me with a cigarette.

08:59.708 --> 09:01.882
He made me smoke the whole
pack right in front of him.

09:01.950 --> 09:03.216
I say we take him back to the grave

09:03.285 --> 09:06.602
