09:30.061 --> 09:32.159
I think I have a solution.

09:32.501 --> 09:35.960
KARL: So, I said to him, "I
already paid for a fill-up.

09:36.034 --> 09:37.800
I'm paying for air, too?"

09:37.869 --> 09:38.968
