no. Enough is enough.

09:51.263 --> 09:53.472
Well, here we are.

09:53.497 --> 09:54.951
Oh, can I finish the story?

09:55.053 --> 09:56.786
- Yeah, sure.
- Okay.

09:56.855 --> 10:00.790
So, I just left. Right? I just drove off

10:00.859 --> 10:02.649
