know, I kind of cooled down.

10:05.385 --> 10:08.664
I came back, right, to apologize.

10:08.733 --> 10:11.701
But Dane already finished
his shift. (LAUGHS)

10:11.770 --> 10:13.035
- He was gone.
- No way.

10:13.138 --> 10:17.807
I come back the next day, right,
with a cup of coffee for him.

10:17.876 --> 10:21.336
I got it for free in
the lobby at a hotel.

10:21.422 --> 10:25.521
Regardless, he appreciated the gesture.

10:25.575 --> 10:27.621
- Right?
- Yeah.

10:27.646 --> 10:30.720
And it just... (GRUNTS)
it just shows you.

10:30.789 --> 10:33.956
I mean, think about
that. It just shows you.

10:34.058 --> 10:37.693
- It shows all of us.
- Yeah.

10:38.105 --> 10:40.840
Worth the wait. Worth the wait.

10:40.865 --> 10:43.733
So, uh, guess this is it.

10:44.207 --> 10:45.902
- Yep.
- Hey,

10:46.004 --> 10:47.970
