12:00.333 --> 12:01.299
So, I'll see you later.

12:01.324 --> 12:02.945
It's period stuff.

12:03.014 --> 12:04.847
Yeah.

12:05.878 --> 12:08.503
MELISSA: So, you thinking
of coming back anytime soon?

12:08.933 --> 12:10.887
